channel.title: How Do I set up my no-ip?
channel.description: OK I got an account. I got my server of course. So I did this. Runserver bat, refresh host list, click on terroristscape.no-ip.biz, and smily is blushing. THen I tried to log on to my other computer but It wont let me. It says server must be down. Tell me whats wrong?[br][size=1]Posted on: January 21, 2007, 03:33:16 PM[/size][hr][size=70pt]SOME1 ANSWER![/size]
